# changing windows focus

## changing window focus within space
ctrl + shift - up   : yabai -m window --focus north
ctrl + shift - down : yabai -m window --focus south
ctrl + shift - left : yabai -m window --focus west
ctrl + shift - right: yabai -m window --focus east

## change focus between external displays
ctrl + shift + cmd - left : yabai -m display --focus west
ctrl + shift + cmd - right: yabai -m display --focus east

## swap windos
ctrl + shift - y   : yabai -m space --mirror y-axis
ctrl + shift - x   : yabai -m space --mirror x-axis

## maximize window
ctrl + shift - f:  yabai -m window --toggle zoom-fullscreen
ctrl + shift - b : yabai -m space --balance
# change space
cmd - 1 : yabai -m space --focus 1
cmd - 2 : yabai -m space --focus 2
cmd - 3 : yabai -m space --focus 3
cmd - 4 : yabai -m space --focus 4
cmd - 5 : yabai -m space --focus 5
